markets.title: Will above people watch the Big Game?
markets.subtitle: :: More than 115,096,000 viewers
markets.rules_primary: If above 115096000 persons watch the pro football championship in 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The data used to resolve the market is the Total Viewers P2+ according to Nielsen. Last year's value can be found here: https://www.nielsen.com/news-center/2024/super-bowl-lviii-draws-123-7-million-average-viewers-largest-tv-audience-on-record/
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire after the data is released.
